Package: rtui
Title: TUI Framework for R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Léopold", "Guyot", , "leopold.guyot@uclouvain.be", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A declarative terminal user interface (TUI) framework for R,
    backed by the FTXUI C++ library via Rcpp. Define apps with a UI
    component tree, a server function, and reactive input/output updates.
